name: Gas Mask
description: You can't give up on yourself even if it's the apocalypse. Use a facial mask in there.

name: Head-Mounted Miner Light
description: Have you decided to become a beacon to guide others? 3,2,1ï¿½ Lovely! The enemy has spotted you!

name: Dirty Coat
description: Stains could be a sort of badge of honor for clothes, the way scars are for humans.

name: Dusty Badge
description: Sooner or later we'll wipe off the dust, just as how we always wash away our shame with blood.

name: Muddy Pants
description: Until we see the light of dawn, we'll have to keep wallowing through blood and mud... But look on the bright side - we can change out of these pants once we get to the finishing point.

name: Male Head
description: A short hairstyle for the workplace - modest but no less fashionable.

name: Female Head
description: A by-the-book long hairstyle - pleasing but could easily get caught in strange things.

name: Griffin Custom Beret
description: It can quickly help the person who sees you identify you quickly. That's pretty much its only use other than being a decoration.

name: Uniform Coat (Male)
description: Extremely sweat-absorbant, you won't have sweat rolling down your back when facing your enemies in it.

name: Uniform Coat (Female)
description: Extremely heat-retaining, you won't get chills down your spine when facing your enemies in it.

name: New Recruit Badge
description: This is your first triumph. Cherish it.

name: Long Black Pants
description: They look just like any other pair of long pants, but are very durable.

name: Black Skirt
description: It looks just like any other office skirt, but is actually a skort that allows plenty of mobility.

name: Summer Leisure Male Head
description: A haircut especially for taking pictures on vacations - understated but smart.

name: Summer Leisure Female Head
description: A haircut especially for taking pictures on vacations - simple but pretty.

name: Beach Shades
description: Sunlight, even if it's artificial, deserves proper respect.

name: Beach Bod (Male)
description: You underwent such long and hellish torture all for this moment. C'mon, don't be shy and show off your muscles!

name: Double Strap Bikini
description: Feast your eyes! This to-die-for figure is the reason why you've braved death time and time again.

name: Summer Sentiments Accessory
description: Being ceremonious means doing the most complicated thing to experience the simplest joy.

name: Swim Trunks
description: Loose shorts perfect for enjoying sunshine and the beach.

name: Beach Sandals
description: Footwear for enjoying the beach. Remember to give them a rinse before you leave.

name: Special Ops Protective Helmet
description: A component that protects your head from a sneak attack from the back.

name: Special Ops Protective Mask
description: A component that protects your face from a head-on slap.

name: Special Ops Protective Top
description: A component that protects your torso from backstabs and gut punches.

name: Military Rucksack
description: A well-designed rucksack with a large capacity that does not weigh you down.

name: Special Ops Protective Pants
description: A component that protects your legs from being leg sweeps and ELID subjects that won't let go of your leg.

name: Summer Night's Refreshing Swept-Back Hair
description: A cool, short haircut for enjoying the summer night. Let the wind kiss your forehead.

name: Moonlight Ornamented Braid
description: An elegant braid for enjoying the summer night. Let the wind kiss your cheeks.

name: Summer Night Festival Headwear
description: We are trying to use hastily - made decorations to deceive the night which has watched us for millennia.

name: Summer Night Yukata Top
description: A light yukata that's easy to wear. It breathes very well.

name: Moonlight Yukata Top
description: A light yukata that's easy to wear. It is decorated with beautiful designs.

name: Moonlight Japanese Paper Lantern
description: The Moon asks the lantern: Since you knew that siding with the humans would make you so weak, why do you still illuminate them, oh Sun?

name: Summer Night Geta
description: Use your geta to strike up a beat while chasing dreams tonight.

name: Moonlight Dreamscape Bottom
description: There's no need to chase the night and dreams when you can entice them to stay with beauty.

name: Fission Halo
description: Don't be ashamed. This is proof of your almighty power.

name: Hairsprayed Big-bro Pompadour
description: I greased my hair up just to keep the sun off my eyes. No other reason. It just happens to look a LITTLE BIT like a pompadour. It's not a pompadour. Why would I have a pompadour? I'm not a delinquent, after all.

name: Blow-dried Big-sis Untied Hair
description: My hair looks like I've been out in a typhoon??? I spent two hours blow-drying it carefully!!! TWO WHOLE HOURS!

name: Essential Tool for Going Out
description: The sun is dazzling today, but with my sunglasses, I'll be even more radiant.

name: Big-bro's Sure-win Baseball Shirt
description: The sovereign is also naturally a trendsetter. If this isn't trendy, I'll make it so.

name: Big-sis's Invincible Sailor Suit
description: I've beaten all these trendsetters as I said I would, so now I'm the new trendsetter.

name: Quality Delinquent Toy
description: Brand new product made of carbon fiber! Elegant design! Feels great in the hand! Realistic feedback! Tailor-made for you, who keep your sunglasses on even at night! New product promotion!

name: Jeans that Have Seen Victory in a Brawl
description: The first step of showing respect to your senpai is to wear your senpai's jeans to a brawl!

name: Flying Kick that Sweeps the Whole Street Away
description: These obsolete rules are all utter nonsense! Watch me break them all with my invincible flying kick!

name: Blood Moon on Halloween - Legendary Headpieces
description: Mysterious headpieces that only appear on Halloween. Apparently, there is a terrifying legend behind every single one of them...

name: Delicate Curls
description: A meticulously prepared hairstyle. Show everyone a different side of yourself.

name: Energetic Ponytail
description: Tie your hair into a ponytail and reminisce... That energetic class captain who's nerdy, long-winded, and violent... I wonder how she's doing now?

name: Party Headdress
description: Finding it hard to fit it? Then throw a party! Put these on and join the fun - Got it? There are things you'll never notice if you don't approach others.

name: Winter Coat
description: A coat that repels both cold wind and strong enemies. The thick fur gives both warmth and sense of security.

name: Warm Jacket
description: Absolute warmth can be extremely comforting. One must prepare for every possibility before facing a challenge.

name: Surprise To-Be-Delivered
description: Put these gifts over your shoulders and deliver the surprise! But don't throw the sacks... It's a pain to reorganize them.

name: Wear-Resistant Pants
description: First of all, they are heat-retaining. Second of all, they're durable! You can give it your all no matter where or when, melting away the cold with your fiery spirit.

name: Winter Shorts
description: Foolhardy people are woeful. Only those with the courage to take challenge head-on are heroes... Perfect with other winter essentials.

name: Refreshing short layered haircut
description: A refreshing choppy hairstyle. A small change could be the start of something new.

name: Lively twintails
description: Twintails that make an impression. Not as dignified as you usually are, but there's a certain sense of novelty to them. Go and show the Dolls your new look!

name: New Year worship headpiece
description: On this day, people pray for a good harvest and enjoy a happy family reunion. This feeling is so fervent people often can't make sense of it...until they watch their friends and loved ones set off once again on their journey. At that moment, it occurs to them what this feeling is - hope. May all be well in the coming year.

name: Short mandarin jacket
description: As we clean out our rooms and organize our belongings, objects of the past encourage us to keep going forward, though of course they may also hold us back - then let us immerse ourselves in reminiscence on this last day of the year. It's also very important to reflect on where we are.

name: New Year Qipao
description: A Commander's attire inspired by the traditional qipao. It's still very warm as the scarf that comes with it is designed with thermal technology...though it isn't meant to flap about and ruin your hairstyle.

name: Auspicious accessories
description: Welcome a sunny spring and celebrate a new and auspcious year! Adorn yourself with heirloom jewelry and wish everyone a happy new year!

name: Fleece-lined trousers
description: Extra-thick pants for the cold spell. Wearing them, you can safely brave the blizzard...or bang snaps.

name: High heels
description: These high heels have been espcially modified. Your feet won't feel tired even after wearing them for an entire day... Sorry, did I say "your feet"? That only applies to Dolls.

name: Pickled Head
description: Have you had enough of working so hard? Yearning for a life without perpetual panda eyes? Keep going! Your work will be over soon!

name: Casual Short Hair
description: When your hair is liberated from hair gel, your brain also relaxes.

name: Untied Shoulder-Length Hair
description: When you take off the hair tie, your thoughts are also liberated.

name: Sleeping Aid
description: These don't actually make you sleep, but at least they can deceive your brain into thinking, "That's right, I'm about to sleep."

name: Silk Pajamas Top
description: The value of silk isn't just in the texture, but also in the sense of comfort brought by its price. Look, this is the reward for my hard work - both the loose-fitting clothes and the time for relaxation.

name: Silk Nightie
description: The value of silk isn't just in the price, but also in the sense of comfort brought by its texture. Whenever I'm here wearing this, I don't have to worry about how other people think of me. I just have to relax.

name: Pillow of Sweet Dreams
description: No matter how long humans live, we're nothing more than the youngest of children to the stars. Embrace the truth that we can only sleep tight when we have something to rely on, and hold onto this pillow.

name: Silk Pajamas Pants
description: Pants aren't always necessary, but it doesn't hurt to wear them either. At least when the delivery man knocks on your door like a maniac, you won't have to search frantically through your bed for something to cover yourself.

name: Cotton Socks
description: It's usually necessary to wear pants, but it doesn't hurt to not wear them either. Why do something pointless for someone else's benefit on your home turf? Socks are much more comfy than pants.

name: Crown of Shared Bounties
description: If you're happy and you know it eat donuts - munch, munch! If you're doleful and you know it eat ice cream - slurp, slurp...

name: Concert Lightstick
description: Illuminating the night with starlight in support of their idols is a fan's romantic gesture.

name: Nova Cap
description: A limited-edition retro cap for commemorating a space organization that once existed.

name: Red & Blue Hat of Bliss
description: The genius is on the left, the maniac on the right. As for which is left and which is right, it all comes down to which direction you're facing.

name: Practical Short Hair
description: This short hairstyle isnï¿½t exactly elegant, but it can save you some time in making yourself presentable ï¿½ every second is a matter of life and death when it comes to an ambush.

name: Braid of Self-Control
description: Keeping your hair long in wartime is an act of prayer ï¿½ you pray for the advent of peace. Though we might no longer be young by then...we still have the right to be beautiful.

name: Accessory of Fire and Blood
description: Take your pick of what you want to wear on your head. It will embody your faith and accompany you as you charge through fire and blood, until you triumphï¿½or until your head becomes an ornament to someone else.

name: Defender Cuirass
description: A light but sturdy cuirass is essential. The smith has sown their blessings of triumph into the armor thread by thread as they pray for your victories and safe return.

name: Oath-Bearer Cuirass
description: A light but sturdy cuirass is essential. It will make its mark in history along with you, whom it has sworn to protect. It will bear witness as you fulfill your oath and attain eternal glory.

name: Personal Weapon
description: A wieldy weapon thatï¿½s also practical on the battlefield can save your life and even defend your dignity.

name: Defender Greaves
description: Greaves may be a pain to put on, but it will significantly increase your chances of survival on the battlefield. As stray arrows bounce off your greaves, do you think of the prayers of the one who dressed you in them?

name: Oath-Bearer Greaves
description: Greaves may be a pain to put on, but it will significantly increase your chances of survival on the battlefield. As a dagger is deflected by your greaves, do you recall your vow to survive till the very end?

name: Wanderer's Ponytail
description: Sir, buy this expensive hair tie! Even if you haven't washed your hair for three days, it will still make you look cool and dashing.

name: Homemakerï¿½s Ponytail
description: Madam, buy this ribbon! It isnï¿½t particularly fancy, but it will complement your already radiant beauty.

name: Wind Whisperer
description: Sitting on the top of your head, it converses with the wind and learns of stories unknown to written history.

name: On-Duty Uniform
description: During times of turmoil, this was the attire of a protector. Now, it can also protect the tummy that you got from not working out.

name: Hostess' New Dress
description: This is meant to be a pinafore that introduces new desserts at a shop in a bustling city. Now, it only serves to make the shop owner look cute.

name: Banner of Conviction
description: When there are noise restrictions in the city, one can only make their proclamations known through a banner! Leasing out fantastic Griffin ad slot!

name: Dignified Hakama
description: Donï¿½t think about how much fabric it took to create this piece of garment. Being wasteful is a civilianï¿½s prerogative during affluent times.

name: Convenient Clogs
description: Even the cheapest clogs have to be sturdier than those made in ancient times. As technology advances, our pace grows steadier.

name: Abstract Masque
description: commander_uniform-20002820

name: Monster Overlord
description: The one in command should save an eye for the everlasting night that will fall any time.

name: Salon-Recommended Short Hair
description: A hairstyle based on what salons tend to recommend. The best way to blend in with a crowd is to keep up with the fashion trend.

name: Simple Traditional Braid
description: A hairstyle demonstrated by fashion influencers. The best way to blend in with a crowd is to turn yourself into a stereotypical beauty.

name: Wind-Resistant Headgear
description: A good design has to be both trendy and practical. That's probably why this hat is reinforced with steel plates.

name: Tactical Outdoor Jacket (Armband Version)
description: An intricate tactical outdoor jacket with reflective strips for identifying allies in the dark and drawing enemy fire away from them.

name: Tactical Outdoor Jacket (Print Version)
description: An intricate tactical outdoor jacket with printed fluorescent patterns for identifying allies in the dark and drawing enemy fire away from them.

name: Tactical Backpack
description: Your gear is your most reliable support on this journey. Have you figured out what it is that you need - survival, carnage, or retirement?

name: Special Ops Pants (Uniform)
description: Designer: Just because there are protective knee pads doesn't mean the wearer should surrender and kneel.

name: Special Ops Pants (Jeans)
description: Designer: May they protect your legs so that you will always get back on your feet and face new challenges.

name: Spare Headband
description: Gr G36 has many of the same headband. Before her younger sister destroys them all, she starts making a new batch, and every single one looks completely identical.

name: Iron Will
description: You have faced countless battles that were a massive pain in the neck, but it seems to be especially bad this time...

name: Gentleman's Chapel
description: A gentleman never neglects his own appearance â he takes care of it like his chapel.

name: Lady's Garden
description: A lady never neglects her own visage â she tends to it like her garden.

name: British Etiquette
description: Welcome to London, traveller.

name: Times Trench Coat (M)
description: "What's in the Times today?" "Same old, same old."

name: Times Trench Coat (F)
description: "This city is always the same; it never changes. That's nice." "Not at all, it's too boring."

name: Detective's Partner
description: On top of great intellect, the ability to vanquish criminals is also essential to a brilliant detective â each famous detective has their own way of achieving this.

name: Suit Pants
description: A suit is the modern knight's armor â this is no exaggeration at all.

name: Stocking
description: Mind where you're looking, or this leg will send you flying before you even know it.

name: Balloon of Brilliance
description: The value of a souvenir is determined by the sentiment it carries. It is alright for some things to burn brilliantly before going out - they don't have to last forever.

name: Regal and Exquisite Headpiece
description: An exquisite headpiece crafted meticulously with peerless workmanship.

name: Colorful and Dazzling Clothing
description: This extraordinary outfit is defined by its perfectly tailored silhouette and precious fabric of top-tier quality.

name: Magic Wire
description: When you are always making risky gambles, do you even remember the weight that life carries?

name: Lone Wolf
description: In the darkness of night, when the masses are entranced by the dazzling fireworks, it is the red eyes and white hair glistening in the moonlight that illuminate the lone wolf's eyes.

name: Lost Lamb
description: In the moonlight, when the masses are entranced by the dazzling fireworks, it is the shadows and sharp claws lurking in the darkness of night that guide the lost lamb home.

name: Merrymaker Decoration
description: On such a joyful night, a group of footloose merrymakers are essential!

name: "Nightstalker" Parka
description: "Black fur, black parkaâ¦ Don't you find it dull?" "...Black is the dignity of a loner."

name: "Worshipper" Parka
description: "Both your fur and your clothes are dazzlingly white. Isn't it hard to keep everything clean?" "...Please don't judge me with the standard of single men who never bother to do their laundry."

description: "Super-duper generous prizes! Play more, win more! The stall owner is losing big-time!" "What? Difficulty levels and tickets? Where's your sense of fun, kiddo?!"

name: "Nightstalker" Pants
description: The dark shadow flitting by in the moonlight is a bundle of tightly wrapped-up muscles.

name: "Worshipper" Shorts
description: The white flash whisking by in the darkness of night is nature being liberated.

name: A Guide's Gratification
description: Those sun-lit smiles are proof that they have illuminated the way in the pitch-dark night.

name: Sparkling Future
description: "New pilots of the Griffin Rebels are reporting for duty! Let's fight for the shining beacon in a brave new world, Commander!" Those sparkling eyes are filled with hope for the future.

name: Imprint of War
description: "I have nothing against you naÃ¯ve simpletons, but remember this, rookies â the battlefield isn't a place for glory; it is hell on earth." Her one remaining eye, scarred by war, burns with bitterness.

name: Gift of the Trailblazer
description: "Uh, leaving aside how you managed to get your hands on all this equipment, rookieâ¦ Are you sure putting them on your face won't cause any interdimensional problem?"

name: Griffin Rebel Coat
description: It may not be able to withstand the cold of vast, empty space, but the tiny bit of warmth it provides can give solace to those whose heart is ravaged by war.

name: Griffin Rebel Uniform
description: The moment you don this dark crimson uniform, you must become a shield that protects those who cannot defend themselves until the day we finally have peace.

name: Experimental Equipment
description: "This isâ¦a rocket launcher that could decimate an entire army in the old age...and a source weapon from another galaxyâ¦? Commander, are you sure you want to entrust these weapons to me?!" "Use them well. The next batch of experimental supplies might not be so usefulâ¦"

name: Rebel Uniform Pants
description: Just keep striving toward your merciful vow and never stop moving, and the path beneath your feet will extend to infinityâ¦ But before doing anything, you need a robust pair of shoes.

name: Rebel Uniform Skirt
description: The path to peace is not easy, but even if you are deeply entrenched in the swamp of war, your beautiful vision will never be tarnished â neither will your grace and virtue as a female warrior.

name: Unruly Bobcut
description: That oppressive attitude is the harshest defense one can muster, just like how a porcupine must prick up the sharp quills it wears to protect its fragile heart.

name: Slapdash Styling
description: That smiling face is his most covert probe of others, just like how the red fox hides its wariness under its blazing pelt.

name: Hidden Hawkeye
description: These glasses won't be removed easily unless there's no other choice, because hiding these eagle eyes is the last pity they show to those spoiling for a fight.

name: Ace Jacket (Male)
description: "Why do the MPs ignore his rulebreaking?" "If you knew what those three badges on his chest meant, you wouldn't be asking that..."

name: Huntress' Leather Jacket (Female)
description: "Pilot, where is your regimental jacket?" "I'm guessing this is my uniform, so what do you think, Sir?"

name: Final Defense Line
description: Cut the paracords and celebrate for a few seconds before running at top speed. Hold this final defense line and this pistol that's lost its magazine.

name: Special Ops Uniform Pants
description: War doesn't show the elite any favoritism. Sometimes what gives you a second chance at life is entirely due to ample preparation on your part.

name: Ranger's Kevlar Pants
description: Amateurs think it's plain and ordinary, but have you realized that it is stab proof and fire resistant, as well as being upgradable at any time?

name: Dandy Side Part
description: This devil-may-care long hairstyle attracts a lot of compliments from your colleagues, but the truth is, you're only keeping such a large fringe to cover up your gradually receding hairline.

name: Mature Long Hair
description: These natural waves require a lot of careful maintenance, but the truth is, only such a voluminous hairstyle can cover up your gradually thinning hair.

name: Surprise of Life
description: The daily life of an office worker may be dull and full of drudgery, but you should nevertheless try to break up the humdrum and introduce some sense of novelty in your life.

name: Future Expectations (M)
description: How do you look more handsome and dandy in a regular suit? On top of having a muscular build, you should also show off your suspenders. That's what it says in fashion magazines at least.

name: Present Enjoyment (F)
description: How do you add a dash of casualness to formal wear? On top of rolling up your sleeves, you should tuck your shirt in with a twist. That's what fashion bloggers say at least.

name: Random Accessory
description: It's pretty normal for a passing office worker to be carrying such stuff, right?

name: Business Hot Pants
description: To the general public, this kind of aesthetic is still a bit ahead of its time, but you must have faith that you will become a trailblazing trendsetter.

name: Wish-Making Leather Shoes
description: The bows on the shoes are like tiny wings that symbolize bygone dreams. You hope they will break free and soar towards freedom.

name: MirrorÂ Universe
description: Griffin,Â remoteÂ signalÂ optimalâallÂ clear.Â LadiesÂ andÂ gentlemen,Â areÂ youÂ readyÂ toÂ seeÂ theÂ universeÂ withÂ yourÂ ownÂ eyes?

name: ExtraterrestrialÂ StarÂ Systems
description: TrustÂ me,Â theÂ momentÂ youÂ flyÂ upÂ intoÂ space,Â yourÂ lookÂ willÂ setÂ aÂ completelyÂ newÂ trend!

name: PlanetariumÂ Souvenir
description: They'reÂ inspiredÂ byÂ theÂ astronauts'Â busyÂ andÂ interestingÂ lives...whichÂ involveÂ fryingÂ eggs,Â bingingÂ TVÂ shows,Â andÂ receivingÂ aliens.

name: TouchÂ theÂ Stars
description: ThisÂ spacesuitÂ willÂ protectÂ youÂ fromÂ allÂ harm,Â unlessÂ youÂ catchÂ aÂ meteoriteÂ withÂ yourÂ bareÂ hands...Â Don'tÂ tellÂ meÂ youÂ actuallyÂ planÂ onÂ doingÂ that!

name: InterstellarÂ Travel
description: TheÂ spaceshipÂ hasÂ nowÂ reachedÂ escapeÂ velocity.Â BeforeÂ weÂ arriveÂ atÂ ourÂ destination,Â spendÂ someÂ timeÂ toÂ getÂ usedÂ toÂ theÂ sensationÂ ofÂ beingÂ inÂ aÂ zero-gÂ environment.

name: LifeÂ SupportÂ System
description: AnÂ essentialÂ pieceÂ ofÂ equipmentÂ forÂ spacewalk.Â TheÂ musicalÂ instrument?Â OneÂ mustÂ findÂ someÂ waysÂ toÂ entertainÂ themselvesÂ inÂ theÂ isolationÂ ofÂ space~!Â TheÂ tentacle?Â JustÂ aÂ giftÂ fromÂ anÂ alien~!

name: CruisingÂ inÂ Space
description: MaybeÂ I'mÂ goingÂ forward,Â maybeÂ I'mÂ goingÂ backward.Â OneÂ mustÂ notÂ loseÂ theirÂ senseÂ ofÂ directionÂ inÂ aÂ differentÂ dimension.

name: WarpÂ Speed
description: IfÂ weÂ couldÂ travelÂ fasterÂ thanÂ theÂ speedÂ ofÂ light,Â IÂ wouldÂ likeÂ toÂ trekÂ acrossÂ theÂ universeÂ inÂ theÂ endlessÂ timeÂ thatÂ IÂ had.

name: Rhythm of Speed
description: I'm all warmed up and ready for a run! Let's start with a song that has a nice beat... Tsk, this one won't do. Skip... Hm... Skip... Skip...

name: Dream of Vigor
description: Strands of hair swing back and forth with every step, partitioning the morning light, making it glint as it bounces off the cute hair accessory.

name: Sweating Like A Pig
description: Sunscreen, recording gear, and clear vision are all essentials for working out.

name: Flaming Spirit
description: Vigorous like a hammering heart, fiery like burning passion.

name: Spirited Dance
description: Light as a swallow, fast as a hare.

name: Builder of Strength
description: Please use training tools correctly. If you're looking for photography props, please show yourself out over there.

name: Supersonic Leap
description: You need to move your legs to traverse the distance. No sports gear, no matter how fancy, can replace your effort.

name: Nimble Twirl
description: When you move your legs to dance or run, the shadow you cast on the ground is nimble like a bird.
